<D>__{merry & pippin aaaaagh! boromir! boromir!}
<A>__{lurtz aims his bow at boromir's heart... suddenly aragorn charges at him, smashing the bow with his sword. they lock into a deadly battle. aragorn cuts lurtz down and races towards boromir, who lies slumped against a tree...uruk hai arrows sticking out of his chest. at least 20 dead uruk hai lie heaped around boromir. his horn lies at his feet...cloven in two.}
